{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7603ba0926","title":"和苏班德里约的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ec01de2fd5","index":0,"year":1965,"month":1,"day":27,"articleId":"7603ba0926"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[{"id":"cd57d257af","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7603ba0926","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"苏班德里约（1914-2004），当时任印度尼西亚共和国外交部部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3f68f296a5","type":"title","text":"和苏班德里约的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7603ba0926"},{"id":"cd57d257af","type":"paragraph","text":"好的拿来，坏的丢掉。无论是本国的或外国的都一样，只能批判地接受，不能教条主义，照搬。这样才有希望。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7603ba0926"},{"id":"c347b83717","type":"paragraph","text":"军事学校办得一场糊涂，正在整理。过去没有军事学校，可好了。打了几十年仗，就是没有军事学校。我们的军队百分之九十以上是不识字和小学程度的。国民党尽办军事学校，什么陆军大学毕业，就是我们这些不识字的兵打倒了它。我们各军区的司令过去都是老粗嘛。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7603ba0926"},{"id":"8cc2c3668f","type":"paragraph","text":"进军事学校的时间太长了。蒋介石办的黄埔军校，五个月入伍训练，四个月学校毕业。蒋介石的军队主要就是这些人还比较能打，陆军大学毕业的实在不能打。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7603ba0926"},{"id":"d822831b17","type":"paragraph","text":"我们有陆军大学吗？（口口口：有高等军事学校。）那就危险了。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7603ba0926"},{"id":"1931f4d08c","type":"paragraph","text":"（口口口：现在要缩短时间了。现在我们大体上就是实现抗大的方针，四至六个月毕业。工程技术学校，要学技术，可能时间长些。）","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7603ba0926"},{"id":"b5443b7b95","type":"paragraph","text":"书可以读一点，但是读多了害人，的确害人。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7603ba0926"},{"id":"2344363c68","type":"paragraph","text":"是革命斗争培养干部。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7603ba0926"}],"page":{"id":"45a22b5fd7","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"7603ba0926","start":468,"end":468}}}},"__N_SSG":true}